Check `.ai-sync/PROGRESS.md` to avoid redoing completed work.

# Project: eCollabs

Collaborative music platform. Next.js 14 + Convex + Clerk + Tailwind/shadcn.

## Commands
- `npm run dev` + `npx convex dev` — dev servers (run simultaneously)
- `npm run build` — production build
- `npx tsc --noEmit` — type-check (always run, build ignores type errors)

## Conventions
- Glassmorphism design system: `glassmorphism`, `surface-elevated`, `glass-hover`
- All dialogs: `className="glassmorphism border-0"`
- Convex pattern: queries with `useQuery()`, mutations with `useMutation()`
- File uploads: Convex storage (`generateUploadUrl` → POST → storageId)
- Path alias: `@/*` = project root
- `convex/_generated/` is auto-generated — never edit

## Architecture
- `app/(root)/` — authenticated pages in DashboardLayout
- `app/(auth)/` — Clerk sign-in/sign-up
- `convex/` — all backend logic (no Next.js API routes)
- `components/` — React components
- `components/ui/` — shadcn primitives
